name: My Links :-)
short_description:
Healthclubsathome are the leading suppliers of pre owned commercial fitness equipment in Europe.

With more than 5500 machines in stock we can supply all makes and models for the most competitive prices-anywhere!

All machines are serviced by our team of experienced and highly skilled engineers and come with a full parts and labour warranty for your complete peace of mind.

Our clients range from Premiership Football Clubs and Players, TV Celebrities, Private Health Clubs to clients at home.

We export to many European countries, and have recently received enquiries from as far a field as Pakistan, South Africa and Argentina.

We have contracts with some of the most prestigious Leisure companies in the UK.

We have some of the most comprehensive stock in Europe with over 5000 treadmills, bikes, steppers, rowers and cross trainers stored in 15 warehouses in the Peterborough area.
